Symbol.Script_3D:
! Linear Slot Diffuser
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, sMat
IF useSysMat AND MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] <> "0" THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- TRANSFORMATION --- !
XFORM MEP_Position[2][1], MEP_Position[3][1], dZx, MEP_Position[1][1], MEP_Position[2][2], MEP_Position[3][2], dZy, MEP_Position[1][2], MEP_Position[2][3], MEP_Position[3][3], dZz, MEP_Position[1][3]
addStatus = 0 IF GLOB_CONTEXT > 40 AND GLOB_CONTEXT < 50 THEN addStatus = 1 ENDIF
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ADDz -0.001 PRISM_ 10, 0.001, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 15, -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 15, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 15, prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 15, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -1, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, -1
if gs_panelStyle_m = 2 then PRISM_ 5, 0.051, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, 0.005, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth+0.001, 0.005, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth+0.001, -0.005, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, -0.005, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, 0.005, -1 endif
if gs_panelStyle_m = 3 then PRISM_ 5, 0.051, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 + 0.005, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth+0.001, prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 + 0.005, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth+0.001, prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 - 0.005, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 - 0.005, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 + 0.005, -1 PRISM_ 5, 0.051, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, -prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 + 0.005, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth+0.001, -prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 + 0.005, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth+0.001, -prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 - 0.005, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, -prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 - 0.005, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth-0.001, -prismInsideHalfDepth * 1/3 + 0.005, -1 endif
DEL 1
EXTRUDE 5, 0, 0, dTHeight, addStatus+2+16+32, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 0, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, -1 ELSE ADDz -0.001
POLY_ 10, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 1, -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 1, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 1, prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 1, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -1, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 1, -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 1, -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 1, prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 1, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, -1
PRISM_ 5, dTHeight+0.001, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, -1 DEL 1 ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 12
DEL TOP
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Linear Slot Diffuser
CALL "MEP_m_RequestPlanViewGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_symbtype_2D_m CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
HptsUnIDBeginForConnEnds = 30000
hceID_1 = HptsUnIDBeginForConnEnds+100 call "2dmacro" parameters all, type_symb = 1 if show_axis then hotspot2 0,0 end endif unID = 1 IF ABS(dZz-1) < EPS THEN ADD2 MEP_Position[1][1], MEP_Position[1][2] ROT2 dirAngOnXYPlane
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
IF gs_symbtype_2D_m = 1 OR gs_symbtype_2D_m = 2 THEN ! Realistic, Electric HOTSPOT2 prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 1, -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 1, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 1, prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 1, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF
RECT2 prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth
IF gs_symbtype_2D_m = 3 THEN END ! RCP
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = 1, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1 = ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 12 DEL 2 ELSE
HOTSPOT2 outCoords[4][1], outCoords[4][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[5][1], outCoords[5][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[6][1], outCoords[6][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[7][1], outCoords[7][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[8][1], outCoords[8][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[9][1], outCoords[9][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[10][1], outCoords[10][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[11][1], outCoords[11][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[12][1], outCoords[12][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[13][1], outCoords[13][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[14][1], outCoords[14][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[15][1], outCoords[15][2], unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 outCoords[1][1], outCoords[1][2], hceID_1
SET FILL gs_fill_type
PEN gs_cont_pen IF gs_fill_pen THEN PEN gs_fill_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 3+32, 4, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 PEN gs_cont_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 2, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ENDIF
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
type_symb = 1 success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "show_axis", show_axis) ! Linear Slot Diffuser
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
prismHalfWidth = dTWidth/2+frameWidth prismHalfDepth = dTDepth/2+frameWidth prismInsideHalfWidth = dTWidth/2 prismInsideHalfDepth = dTDepth/2
! ---------------- ! ! --- Z vector --- ! ! ---------------- !
dZx = -MEP_Position[3][2]*MEP_Position[2][3]+MEP_Position[3][3]*MEP_Position[2][2] dZy = -MEP_Position[3][3]*MEP_Position[2][1]+MEP_Position[3][1]*MEP_Position[2][3] dZz = -MEP_Position[3][1]*MEP_Position[2][2]+MEP_Position[3][2]*MEP_Position[2][1]
! --- dirAngOnXYPlane of the route --- !
IF ABS(dZz-1) < EPS THEN arCosVal = MEP_Position[3][1]/1 IF ABS(arCosVal) > 1 AND SGN(arCosVal) = -1 THEN arCosVal = -1 IF ABS(arCosVal) > 1 AND SGN(arCosVal) = 1 THEN arCosVal = 1 dirAngOnXYPlane = ACS(arCosVal)-90 IF SGN(MEP_Position[3][2]) = -1 THEN dirAngOnXYPlane = 180-dirAngOnXYPlane ENDIF
!!! +++ Transformational Matrix +++ !!!
DIM tMatrix[3][3]
tMatrix[1][1] = MEP_Position[2][1] tMatrix[1][2] = MEP_Position[2][2] tMatrix[1][3] = MEP_Position[2][3]
tMatrix[2][1] = MEP_Position[3][1] tMatrix[2][2] = MEP_Position[3][2] tMatrix[2][3] = MEP_Position[3][3]
tMatrix[3][1] = dZx tMatrix[3][2] = dZy tMatrix[3][3] = dZz
!!! +++ Input Coordinates +++ !!!
PUT ConPosX_1+gs_Connections[1][4]*ConLength_1, ConPosY_1+gs_Connections[1][5]*ConLength_1, ConPosZ_1+gs_Connections[1][6]*ConLength_1 PUT gs_Connections[1][4], gs_Connections[1][5], gs_Connections[1][6] PUT gs_Connections[1][7], gs_Connections[1][8], gs_Connections[1][9]
PUT prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0 PUT -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0 PUT -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0 PUT prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0
PUT prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 0 PUT -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 0 PUT -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 0 PUT prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 0
PUT prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight PUT -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight PUT -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight PUT prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, dTHeight
Coordinates = NSP/3
DIM inCoords[20][3]
FOR cnum = 1 TO Coordinates inCoords[cnum][1] = GET(1) inCoords[cnum][2] = GET(1) inCoords[cnum][3] = GET(1) NEXT cnum
! --- the Matrix Operation, what make the Output-Coordinates
DIM outCoords[20][3]
FOR cnum = 1 TO Coordinates outCoords[cnum][1] = inCoords[cnum][1]*tMatrix[1][1]+inCoords[cnum][2]*tMatrix[2][1]+inCoords[cnum][3]*tMatrix[3][1]+MEP_Position[1][1] outCoords[cnum][2] = inCoords[cnum][1]*tMatrix[1][2]+inCoords[cnum][2]*tMatrix[2][2]+inCoords[cnum][3]*tMatrix[3][2]+MEP_Position[1][2] outCoords[cnum][3] = inCoords[cnum][1]*tMatrix[1][3]+inCoords[cnum][2]*tMatrix[2][3]+inCoords[cnum][3]*tMatrix[3][3]+MEP_Position[1][3] NEXT cnum
z = MEP_Position[1][3]
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z
Symbol.Script_UI:
! Linear Slot Diffuser
UI_DIALOG `Специальные Параметры MEP`
DIM ui_set_str[4][2] ui_set_str[1][1] = "(A) "+`Ширина` ui_set_str[2][1] = "(B) "+`Длина` ui_set_str[3][1] = "(C) "+`Высота` ui_set_str[4][1] = "(D) "+`Длина Соединения`
ui_set_str[1][2] = "dTWidth" ui_set_str[2][2] = "dTDepth" ui_set_str[3][2] = "dTHeight" ui_set_str[4][2] = "ConLength_1"
DIM ui_set_attr[5][9] FOR i = 2 TO 5 FOR j = 1 TO 9 ui_set_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_set_attr[1][1] = 1 ui_set_attr[1][2] = 3 ui_set_attr[1][3] = 220 ui_set_attr[1][4] = 50 ui_set_attr[1][5] = 127 ui_set_attr[1][6] = 90 ui_set_attr[1][7] = 15 ui_set_attr[1][8] = 128 ui_set_attr[1][9] = 23
DIM ui_vis_attr[5][4] FOR i = 1 TO 5 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ui_vis_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_vis_attr[1][1] = 3 ui_vis_attr[1][2] = 1 ui_vis_attr[1][3] = 6 ui_vis_attr[1][4] = 7
ui_vis_attr[2][1] = 1 ui_vis_attr[2][2] = 237 ui_vis_attr[2][3] = 68 ui_vis_attr[2][4] = 14
DIM ui_con_type[1] ui_con_type[1] = 0
IF useSysMat AND MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] <> "0" THEN ui_vis_attr[5][2] = 4 ELSE ui_vis_attr[5][2] = 0 ENDIF
IF MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] = "0" THEN ui_vis_attr[4][2] = 4 ELSE ui_vis_attr[4][2] = 0 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS ALL ui_set_str = ui_set_str, ui_set_attr = ui_set_attr, ui_vis_attr = ui_vis_attr, ui_centerline_vars = 0, ui_con_type = ui_con_type, ui_system_var_pos = 1
setPage = 1 ui_cur_page = 0 FOR j = 1 TO VARDIM1(ui_page_idx) IF ui_page_idx[j] = setPage THEN ui_cur_page = j NEXT j
IF ABS(gs_ui_current_page - ui_cur_page) < EPS THEN UI_PAGE gs_ui_current_page
UI_PICT 1, 25, 45, 156, 200, 1 ENDIF
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "2dmacro" parameters all, type_symb = type_symb ! Linear Slot Diffuser
CALL "MEP_m_RequestPlanViewGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_symbtype_2D_m
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 1 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
IF useSysMat AND MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] <> "0" THEN LOCK "MainBoxMaterial" IF MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] = "0" THEN LOCK "useSysMat"
values "gs_panelStyle" `1 щель`, `2 щели`, `3 щели` values "gs_panelStyle_m" 1, 2, 3
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_panelStyle" then if gs_panelStyle = `1 щель` then gs_panelStyle_m = 1 dTDepth = 0.07 endif if gs_panelStyle = `2 щели` then gs_panelStyle_m = 2 dTDepth = 0.15 endif if gs_panelStyle = `3 щели` then gs_panelStyle_m = 3 dTDepth = 0.23 endif parameters gs_panelStyle_m = gs_panelStyle_m parameters dTDepth = dTDepth else if gs_panelStyle_m = 1 then gs_panelStyle = `1 щель` if gs_panelStyle_m = 2 then gs_panelStyle = `2 щели` if gs_panelStyle_m = 3 then gs_panelStyle = `3 щели` parameters gs_panelStyle = gs_panelStyle endif
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF dTHeight < 0.051 THEN dTHeight = 0.051 VALUES "dTHeight" RANGE [0.051,] IF dTWidth < 0.011 THEN dTWidth = 0.011 VALUES "dTWidth" RANGE [0.011,] IF dTDepth < 0.011 THEN dTDepth = 0.011 VALUES "dTDepth" RANGE [0.011,] VALUES "frameWidth" RANGE [0,] ENDIF
PARAMETERS A = dTWidth+frameWidth*2 PARAMETERS B = dTDepth+frameWidth*2 PARAMETERS zzyzx = dTHeight LOCK "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 1
! --- THE ONLY CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Соединение Конца Воздуховода`
ConDVecX = 0 ConDVecY = -1 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF ABS(MEP_NumConnectionData[1][21] - 2) < EPS THEN VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, MIN(dTWidth-ConWallThickness_1*2, dTHeight-ConWallThickness_1*2)] PARAMETERS ConDepth_1 = ConWidth_1 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_1" ELSE VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, dTWidth-ConWallThickness_1*2] VALUES "ConDepth_1" RANGE (0, dTHeight-ConWallThickness_1*2] ENDIF
VALUES "ConLength_1" RANGE [0, ] VALUES "ConPosX_1" RANGE [-dTWidth/2+ConWidth_1/2+ConWallThickness_1, dTWidth/2-ConWidth_1/2-ConWallThickness_1] PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = -dTDepth/2 PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = dTHeight/2
VALUES "ConWallThickness_1" RANGE [0, MIN((dTWidth-ConWidth_1)/2, (dTHeight-ConDepth_1)/2)] ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF SetProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
FOR k = 1 TO MEP_NumberConnections FOR i = 1 TO 9 j = 1+INT((i-0.5)/3) MEP_NumConnectionData[k][i] = outCoords[j+3*(k-1)][i-3*(j-1)] PARAMETERS MEP_NumConnectionData[k][i] = MEP_NumConnectionData[k][i] NEXT i NEXT k
